{"tid":2042003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[至少3名手足上庭！] 5月30號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-05-29T14:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T16:33:36.000Z","uid":292499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8138d9d57dea2293f25b0f8bee9befb651fb84e3","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 5 月 3 0 日 星期六】<br />\n<br />\n🏛觀 塘 裁 判 法 院 3 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️錢禮主任裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👤梁(28) #新案件（#20200527銅鑼灣 管有攻擊性武器、管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產）<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n🏛粉嶺裁判法院 4 樓 1 庭<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;⚖️蘇文隆署理主任裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👥2名13歲手足 #新案件（#20200528上水 在公眾地方造成阻礙:RB）"},{"pid":"9db4997fb8a7729124a469e19e1509550a284475","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=6a156852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"1daaa8fc7742a85e42d28e213202fe7a9be00ca7","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=96f18e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=e7854573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"a4e387ad653bb86a69169ec3e3f69a0b0196488c","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfvV1rg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfvV1rg.jpg&h=18b9d6ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df7b7490705b718f6769a10e8641af093e91fd0d","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"c9f2493f75e3da9594ffcc6c6cab96cd2abbbc2d","tid":2042003,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d6a95e647f04676ef013fe95aeae53d9f3420ea","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n觀塘裁判法院交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界</strong><br />\n上水：<br />\n277E                        [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n粉嶺：<br />\n277X                        [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n大埔：<br />\n74X 到大老山<br />\n轉乘 89D, 277E/X   [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n馬鞍山：<br />\n89D                          [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n沙田：<br />\n89/B/C/X 到大老山<br />\n轉乘 89D, 277E/X  [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n將軍澳：<br />\n296A                       [觀塘法院]<br />\n坑口、寶林：<br />\n98A                         [觀塘法院]<br />\n青衣、荃灣：<br />\n42C                         [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n葵芳：<br />\n38                           [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n屯門：<br />\n258D, 259D            [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n油塘：<br />\n14B                         [觀塘法院]<br />\n藍田：<br />\n14B, 15A                [觀塘法院]<br />\n慈雲山：<br />\n15A                         [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n黃大仙：<br />\n14, 15, 38, 42C, 258D, 259D   [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n九龍灣：<br />\n14/B, 15/A, 16, 38, 42C, 89D [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n土瓜灣：<br />\n14, 15                     [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n尖沙咀：<br />\n14X, 215X             [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n旺角：<br />\n16, 93K, 296C       [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n深水埗：<br />\n296C                      [觀塘游泳池]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、灣仔：<br />\n619, 641⚠️注意服務時間 [觀塘法院]<br />\n灣仔：<br />\n601, 619, 641            [觀塘法院]<br />\n銅鑼灣：<br />\n601, 619, 671(建議) [觀塘法院]<br />\n東區：<br />\n606                        [觀塘法院]<br />\n鴨脷洲、黃竹坑：<br />\n671                        [觀塘法院]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"9d6569f2a58ee0e12a3b2ece49287f8fce9dd277","tid":2042003,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8b83566b20f9dee7aa9c1530c15ad79549388b2","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n粉嶺裁判法院交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界東</strong><br />\n大埔：73B       [粉嶺名都]<br />\n大埔：73B       [粉嶺法院大樓] **不建議<br />\n上水：79K       [璧峰路]<br />\n打鼓嶺：79K   [粉嶺法院大樓]<br />\n大老山：277X [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界西</strong><br />\n屯門：261       [粉嶺名都]<br />\n青衣：279X    [粉嶺名都]<br />\n大欖：279X    [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n藍田站、觀塘道、彩虹邨：277X  [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后：673 [粉嶺名都]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺相對少對外交通，其他地區需使用黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"92752fd2c62e6d918c157de3846aa8ec194d833b","tid":2042003,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"209976bfd49e41187982c217173d0bebf6bee943","tid":2042003,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"法庭要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852a316112871969e1939bab26ecc3fcb55a57df","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"【保釋及送車位置】<br />\n<br />\n✵送車位位於法院停車場🅿️<br />\n✵揾唔到就圍住法院兜一圈⭕️<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《觀 塘 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（馬路燈前轉）／正門轉右再轉右（見到郵政局轉）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《粉 嶺 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門<br />\n**唯一送車遮陣出出入入都係同一個位<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特別鳴謝被捕人士關注組公海手足cc整合以上資訊</strong>"},{"pid":"96b0b51de5a16c99587ab1aea91417ce86393041","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"法庭星期六繼續要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f1eb7cc360cb000a18ce39d11b421a59dddca9","tid":2042003,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"感謝手足們幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de729dbc85912d69c28